  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821542401-SQ26GKQG6V4RR4BSW9J6/13a-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Recently, <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2q8KTqq\">American Tourister</a> helped me host my first Instameet for WWIM15! We had so much fun at <a href=\"http://www.latimes.com/home/la-hm-tom-dixon-showroom-20160719-snap-story.html\">Tom Dixon in Culver City</a> celebrating <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/kindnessiscolorful/\">#KindnessIsColorful</a>. I started off the day by picking up some giant balloons at our local party store. They just barely fit in my car! Then I headed over to Platform LA to get set up.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.platformla.com/\">Platform LA</a> is one of my favorite places to hang out so it was awesome being able to bring a small group of friends together for some lunch from sweetgreen and some fun photo taking. You can check out <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/kindnessiscolorful/\">#KindnessIsColorful</a> on Instagram to see photos from everyone else as well!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13b-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821578075-4ILYKXGFG6TRW6IQJM4N/13b-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13c-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821578737-VZ7V0M7NYECCR1RCNR52/13c-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13d-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821580948-Z8KDURER6XSMKDK6D0R7/13d-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821581402-J54H099V45WGL1JDS7Q5/13e-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>During the Instameet, I set up a Make and Take station with the watercolor resist tags from my <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AmyTanOnAWhim\">On A Whim product line</a> so everyone could try them out and make a cute luggage tag! All we needed to decorate the tags were some <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2j27LU0\">watercolors</a> and a <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iFLtep\">water brush</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13f-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821648073-HC9JC9IIFZGEQF55ZOUQ/13f-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13g-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821644405-L3S27BNQ86FWQL9YN2G5/13g-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13h-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595821651425-IIQY2N5KRMIY8WKQSJYS/13h-American%2BTourister%2BInstameet%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13i-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Ta